The PsychGeno application itself — its source code, training data, and
trained model weights — is NOT released under this licence. It lives in
private repositories under separate non-public terms. Nothing in this
repository should be read as a grant of rights to the underlying software
or model artefacts.

This project is an educational research demonstrator. Not a medical
device. Not FDA or CE approved. For educational and research purposes
only. Consult a qualified healthcare professional for any health
concerns.
